    "text": "Lombard is currently leading the market in percentage revenue growth, driven by its aggressive consolidation of the Bitcoin liquid staking market. By acquiring Avalanche’s **BTC.b** from Ava Labs, Lombard effectively secured ~57% of total BTC liquid staking market share. This infrastructure pivot allowed **LBTC** to reach $1B in TVL within 92 days, making it the fastest yield-bearing token to hit that milestone.

![Lombard LBTC Performance and Growth Metrics](https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjriemfd/image/upload/v1768031305/veldt/n1xsztpshgdberqttheg.jpg)

